Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew aboard the Quin Zaza\Nis very diverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People who wanted to be in a ship.\NPeople who are on board for certain reasons…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Their origins being different
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with their own circumstances.\NEveryone here became a draker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-... Hey!\NEveryone, there's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, there's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This... this is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanabelle... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... It's as if someone drew it\Nwhile watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that it'd look that good\Nwithout seeing her in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean he saw her like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nah, there's no way.\N-But man...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, this is pretty good…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not bad at all.\NIn fact, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me look too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us look at it some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as it would wither or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Denied!\N-Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder who on earth would draw this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Catching the wind, seizing the shadows."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So... where are we supposed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Oken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With this as a proof...\NCan we establish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's someone spying on\NVanabelle while she sleeps?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's no other believable option.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We have even 4 women aboard,\Nwhich is pretty rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that this lucky-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, this serious situation\Nwould happen sooner or later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, who would have thought
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's someone\Nso brave as to do that to Vannie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The room where the drawing was found was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, Hiro and Gaga's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit is one of those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this has gotten interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Jiro-san\Nwould be capable of something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! Sometimes the most\Nstraight-laced ones are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The engineer's apprentice, Hiro, has\Npretty skillful hands too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and he's pretty gloomy,\Nit could be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And Gaga is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think someone with those looks\Nwould be able to draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, with those ones as our culprits\Nit will be pretty easy to find the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! How shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we get the suspects and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Jiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you draw a portrait of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It is settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit behind this drawing of Vanabelle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it's you, Gaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Wha-!\NWhat are you taking without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you sneaked into the\Nroom of a sleeping beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sly bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a bad loser is kinda lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, confess your crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who drew Vannie-san's portrait?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a misun-... misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are so worked up about it\Nit makes you all the more suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you are as close as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I can't sleep over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are quarreling about\Nsomething irrelevant again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bo-boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That you were so good at drawing, Gaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm drawing these as a journal of things\Nthat happen in the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There's a drawing of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really able to draw this\Nonly from your imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think it's pretty normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means that you weren't peeping at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you keeping this from all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That... that is because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about you draw me\Na nice nude of my type of woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Gaga, one for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything about it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,precisely because of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! From the very beginning I believed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that you, Gaga, wouldn't be\Ncapable of something so low!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You suspected him the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oken-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,With all said and done, I'm glad there isn't\Na bad person aboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are\Nso energetic and gung-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pick a special job for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your back into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally, Takita, you were the one\Nwho jumped to the wrong conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko-san, weren't you also on board\Nwith the idea from minute one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When we finish this I'm gonna\Nhave my arms stiff for 2 days straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that I was off duty today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My hips hurts so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be filthy in no time again anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I doing this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have time for small talk\Nmove those hands instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are so easy on the floor\Nwe are gonna be here till the end of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Vannie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair is unruly as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing it by force will make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Vannie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind dandruff...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all the same inside this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm? What a good smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfumed oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You get this by mixing camellias and dragon incense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon incense?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the mineral obtained from rare secretions\Nthat form inside a dragon's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Takita...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely accustomed to it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the type that can sleep anywhere\Nas long as there's a roof over my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I... sometimes feel a bit lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why am I here right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And going so far as to kill dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do have times of doubt too,\NVannie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought I was more aloof?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... no, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san, you always have\Nthis cool aura around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And your skill catching dragons\Nis second to no one aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that...\NI just had nowhere to belong to on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowhere to belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I had no place for me to belong to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I became skilled in how to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for letting out something so awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You are always eating bread like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the way\Nit soaks in the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um!\NWe have pickled cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go only eating\Nstew and potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san! Pass me your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so pickled that is\Nsure to be sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fermented precisely\Nbecause nobody's eating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, I'm committed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Committed to eat only the\Nthings I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and pass me your plate, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Vannie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Make space for her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-No need to mind yourself with that.\N-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the laundry for you in front\Nof the boys' quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...? You could do that much\Nby yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All chores are for the newbies after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You left laundry\Nto do not so much ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were cleaning the deck\Nthe other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's with that?\N-Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... that, yeah.\NThere's no particular reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-My drawings were...\N-Drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai-...! Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are that rough with it\Nit's gonna end up breaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do this much\Nit doesn't feel like you've actually done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of the lever, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm astonished at the passion\Nyou put into doing laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Vannie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san is doing this\Nby brute force!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, hang out these instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Mika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you... notice something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a good smell coming out or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a smell clear as day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A very delicious smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hidden in the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the lookout to check!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...! Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! We can't see anything from here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure it wasn't the shadow of a cloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To our 8 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably hidden in the clou-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey! Mika, wai-!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a mountain of clouds to our 8.\NIt's behind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do us a favour and raise the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some respect\Nto your deputy captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't on the morning shift, was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a break and behave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!\NDon't go doing whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you listening to me, Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So little space...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks quite big.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I see a dragon so round.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh! It's pretty huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange form...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! All hands on deck! Prepare!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!\NThe dragon waits for no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As one would expect from you, Gibbs,\Nyou don't miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is... looking at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha- What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh... I'm so dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was attacking us with that soundwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it wasn't attacking the ship but us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to aim our bomb lances like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues, it seems that waiting\Nfor it to grow weaker is the better choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we can just wait for it to die like that\Nfor hours on end?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:13:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out to finish it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we have it anchored\Nit is not a matter if we can stand on it or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible, it'll explode your eardrums!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are trying to take its life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have that much fun killing dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... he is so reckless as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the bridge to\Nraise our course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like... the sky is spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Still screaming, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My head is spinning like crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip on yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanabelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone! Finish it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick... put it out of its misery...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I... sometimes feel a bit lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why am I here right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And going so far as to kill dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do have times of doubt too,\NVannie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I had nowhere to belong to on land,\NI became skilled in how to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I had no place for me to\Nbelong to on land...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... all there is to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It has shrunk quite noticeably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Great work out there! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs... I'm participating in the dissection too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even walk straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...\NYou're always so careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you managed to catch it,\Nthere's no point if you die out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow myself to die,\Nnot until I have savored all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunt, dissect and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what all drakers are about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Return peacefully to the clouds\Nand grant us good winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Words for parting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! Stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I found a big rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Ah, it's you Vanabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not snitching food, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your shift over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the liver of the dragon we captured today.\NI put it in the oiling pot along with its fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And secretly cooked it\Nat a low temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't call that snitching food?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind accompanying me for a glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see we have some leftovers of\Npotato and cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you smash these together with a little bit\Nof oil and salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple countryside cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread the pickled cabbage\Non a mold coated with oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then press together\Nliver confit with mashed potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mika.\N-Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When you are hunting dragons\Nyou are always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so much fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I guess it is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you press together the ingredients\Ninside the mold...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you remove it with care,\Ncut it in your desired sized pieces and it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you look at that beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanabelle, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strong, rich and fresh at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like we randomly put this together\Nbut it tastes like proper cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What are you eating there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if I was snitching food!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that Vanabelle made.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not asking you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Back from your shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm freezing all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our turn to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you here and alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-What a rare sight.\N-Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks good, don't mind if I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wai-!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Well, if it's so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Those were all for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie!\NPlease make this again some other time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... if you are happy with something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?\NOn this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I love dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunting dragons, dissecting them\Nand eating them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way we all live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But above all else, it's because\NI get to eat a lot of dragons here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want something good,\Nthere are many other tasty things out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But dragons are the most delicious of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro-san told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You were all eating\Nsomething tasty yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you not yell next to my ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfair! Unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Jiro-san, this goes for you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you excluding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san, don't laugh\Nand tell them off too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Translation: TomoyaNC   Proofreading: akemilena
